-- Finmeccanica Is Seeking New Markets, Chief Executive Tells La Repubblica
-- B y   A l e s s a n d r a   M i g l i a c c i o
-- 2010-11-01T09:06:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/finmeccanica-is-seeking-new-markets-chief-executive-tells-la-repubblica.html
Finmeccanica SpA  wants to increase
sales in markets including Saudi Arabia, India, Oman and Turkey
in order to offset decreased defense spending in Europe and the
U.S., Italian daily La Repubblica reported, citing Chief
Executive Officer Pierfrancesco Guargualini.  To contact the reporter on this story:
